<HEADLINE>
FT  19 OCT 93 / World News in Brief: Fort Knox shootings
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
A gunman, thought to be a retired serviceman, shot dead a man and two women
and wounded two other people at Fort Knox, the US Army base that houses the
country's gold reserves.
</TEXT>
